name: Strange Pigs
description: The Potluck Pigs were out roaming the fields near the Cave at night. Soon on the horizon a strange object came into view. Most shrugged it off as nothing, until it came closer and closer. The pigs began to see the outline of an oblong shape with strangely beautiful lights glimmering and sparkling. For an unknown reason, they felt weirdly drawn to the lights.

The object now hovering above the pasture, opened from underneath, as a beam of light began to pull them one by one into the ship. As the pigs entered, fear began to shoot through the bodies as they saw the restraints on tables and the experimental equipment. It was too late for them, they could no longer stop it and go back. No one could have ever imagined what would happen to the pigs on that ship...

name: Revolutionary Apes
description: Humanity through escapism has turned to psychedelic drugs. Humanity was driven to endangerment through constant gentrification, racism, war, and inequality. In parallel, Apes have broken free of captivity and have reclaimed their position in nature. Through use of Human-made tools/devices, Apes have developed higher cognitive abilities. It would seem that humanity -- tripping off its disposition, has now adopted the mentality of apes. Whereas the society of apes mirrors the modern world of humanity. Though with this adoption of societal values, perhaps ape-kind will also adopt human viciousness and prejudice

name: Strange Gods
description: The Strange Gods were not pleased with what has been happening down on the farm. They have watched as the Strange Ones did unspeakable things to the Potluck Pigs. They will no longer allow life to remain the same. Because of their righteous anger, the Gods declared that they would wipe out the entire population of Potluck Pigs, Strange Ones, and Strange Pigs, unless a sacrifice was made. In an attempt to appease the Strange Gods and to achieve the highest level of deity, You must lay a Potluck Pig, a Strange One, and a Strange Pig at the alter to be sacrificed to save the farm from complete desolation.

name: Nekro Demonz
description: When they first appeared, it was an anomaly. The general consensus was that some freak atomic irradiation incident had transformed a handful of folk into a heresy of nature. Their technicolor appearance gave credence to this theory. As more and more appear, it has become clear that something is actively creating these creatures. Once in a while, you might see an Atomik that you once scavenged with sporting this new, grotesque form. Is it some scientist hellbent of rising in ranks to join the Gods of the Wastes? Or is it something far darker, far older? Is it unnatural magic? Only the NekroVerse holds the answers.

name: Arbiters of the Deep
description: Deep within the labyrinthine like cave system, among the glowing stalagmites of unrefined ore and noxious moss, there sat a throne. With all the impending doom of the unsetting Sun, this moonless and crypt like dungeon was largely undiscovered. Even the creatures were mostly unaware of these powerful cryptids.

Dragon Humanoid Cycloptic Cave Dwellers could be the simplest scientific term given to them.  A bestial mastery, ordained to a species high on the food chain.  They once ruled the skies, earth and subterrain equally and uncontested.
Now forsaken and pushed back to the cave ; there was only one pursuit amongst the warring clans of the Arbiters.  To restore their rightful rule of the Lands, and  seek the power of Gods.

name: Ghoulish Divas
description: The Ghoulish Divas (Fantomized X Potluck Collab):

There was once a group of beautiful women, said to be the Goddesses of the Potluck Realm. Who, desiring youth above all else, discovered mysterious vials that had fallen from the FantomGates. Believing these vials were sent from the Gods and contained the fountain of youth, they consumed them at once. 733 women were changed in an instant. Horrifically mutated into something so dark, so vial... but also granted immortality in this grotesque state. The Ghoulish Divas now wander the realm in perpetuity caged in their own prison of flesh.

name: Roboto
description: The path to perfection has never been easy.)
It was clear that human biology has reached its limits.
What was not clear is how to overcome it.
Theories have been made since the late 20th century.
And soon enough various radicals rushed to this frontier.
People thought that all they got to do is upload their minds to the Internet.
Where are these pioneers now? Stuck in depraved webcam rooms for decades. Pathetic…
On the contrary, we took a different approach.
For years looking for kindred spirits, researchin…our bodies, minds and souls for future ascension.
We fused together top technologies and ancient traditions.
For if the human is stripped from courage, honor,…d microchips – then it`s just the mindless drone.
Our final steps were tough. We remembered how cen…usands of souls, and sought to avoid such a fate.
Eventually, some seers and digital alchemists fro…tion – Potluck Labs – helped us with this matter.
And now we rise in full glory.
More than machines, stronger than humans.
Ignorant fools call us abominations, some of them even try to wipe us out.
Fools….We can overwhelm anyone standing in our way.

name: Shamanic Tribe
description: It had been 7 long months at sea on a giant ship for The Lost Shamanic Tribe of the Old World. They had fled their lands during the massive flood and since then the tribe was searching for a new home. However, on the first day of the new year, one of the Void Angels got a message from The Shaman, saying he was waiting for them to come and live on The Island.  The Void Angel announced the big news to everyone and the ship sailed right to The Island.

This was a big day for The Island as well. The Shaman gathered every islander and they all went to the beach. They set a big fire and around it formed a giant drum circle. One of the Islanders, IlluminatiCongo stood up, walked to the fire and began to chant in ancient words. Some other free sprits jumped to their toes and started dancing. They all got united in a single groove and right at the moment they all synchronized, the giant ship appeared on the horizon.
The Islanders danced until the ship had arrived. And when The Shamanic Tribe landed on the beach, they all joined the groove and the party went on for seven days and seven nights.

name: Evil Family
description: Papa pulled the truck over and turned to look at his Wife, she was asleep and was still covered in blood. Evan and Evie were the in back also sleeping soundlessly. Buttercup was sat in the middle with his head on Papa’s lap. They were all together again, something that Papa thought was never gonna be possible again, he took a deep sigh and took his packet of smokes out of his top pocket, he lit one and took a long deep drag. They were almost clear, almost free, if they could just cross the Canadian Border they’d be set, free to start over. But what if his Dark Passenger wanted more blood? More flesh? Had he created his family’s Dark Passenger’s? Or were they just all cut from the same cloth? Maybe that’s why he and Mama were soul mates, maybe that’s why they had brought to life 2 children many people have called monsters. He finished his smoke and flicked the butt out of the window, checked the magazine in his Glock, put the truck into drive and headed for the border. They’d make it, no matter how many lives they’d have to take to do it…

name: Paint Huffing Degenerates 2
description: The only constant is change... OG PhD boomers, you need to make way for the new generation of Paint Huffing Degens! they've spread like a disease and multiplied by the millions by now. They're meaner, uglier and hornier than ever before! Still Huffing and Puffing till they blow all their brain cells away. New Huff city (previously known as New Huffington) has never seen such chaos and utter madness... Rioting, looting, setting fires and flipping cars is just your average tuesday night in PhD land. The city sign reads 'welcome to New Huff City! ...there's still time to turn around' ...better be quick about it though, they'll steal your wheels while you shift in reverse.
